## Common Anti-Patterns to Avoid

- âŒ Circular dependencies between layers
- âŒ Direct cross-slice imports at same level
- âŒ Business logic in `shared/` layer
- âŒ UI components in `entities/` layer
- âŒ Bypassing Public API (index.ts files)
- âŒ **Monolithic components** over 200 lines
- âŒ **Mixed responsibilities** in single component/function
- âŒ **Logic coupled** to specific UI components
- âŒ **Premature shared extraction** without proven reuse
- âŒ **Domain-specific code** in shared layer
- âŒ **Over-abstraction** of single-use components
- âŒ **Relative import paths** (use absolute paths instead)
- âŒ **Duplicated constants** across multiple files
- âŒ **Hardcoded values** without centralized configuration

